July 22, 2017 1:38 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of BP Investment Management Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BP Investment Management Limited (BPIM) is an asset management arm of BP plc. The firm manages pension funds for its parent company. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investments markets across the globe. The firm typically makes its alternative investments in real-estate and private equity. BP Investment Management was founded in 1936 and is based in London, United Kingdom.


20 Canada SquareLondon,  E14 5NJUnited KingdomFounded in 1936



Phone: 44 20 7496 4000

Fax: 44 20 7496 4630








